00:28:42,500 --> 00:28:44,000
Sikapmu beda akhir-akhir ini.

351
00:28:45,291 --> 00:28:47,458
Pertama, kau meneriaki Nyonya Lim.

352
00:28:48,208 --> 00:28:50,666
Lalu kau marah kepada Yan Hong.

353
