00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:34,125
Jaga dirimu baik-baik.

376
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:37,083
Hati-hati di jalan.

377
00:30:44,125 --> 00:30:45,916
Aku sudah mencari di kamarnya,

